1. *Poštovanje* je osnova svakog odnosa. (Respect is the foundation of every relationship.)

2. Poštujmo *poštovanje* drugih. (Let's respect the respect of others.)

3. Oni koji su nedostojni *poštovanja* nisu vredni pažnje. (Those who are unworthy of respect are not worth attention.)

4. Oni koji ne poštuju *poštovanje* ne mogu imati dobre odnose. (Those who don't respect respect can't have good relationships.)

5. *Poštovanje* je najvažnije u porodici. (Respect is the most important thing in family.)

6. Oni koji poštuju *poštovanje* su u stanju da podignu svoje dete poštovanjem. (Those who respect respect are able to raise their child with respect.)